            <title><![CDATA[青海大通县山洪已致16人遇难36人失联]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/eb7ed09a62bdadbb0b644ae12fb7f1b8.jpg?VersionId=uzkblScl6Bdy5xFivMnY947rrCgoqEhq&amp;itok=EdXauVnj" title="青海西宁市大通县发生山洪灾害，已造成16人遇难36人失联。（央视新闻）
" alt="青海西宁市大通县发生山洪灾害，已造成16人遇难36人失联。（央视新闻）
" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/eb7ed09a62bdadbb0b644ae12fb7f1b8.jpg?VersionId=uzkblScl6Bdy5xFivMnY947rrCgoqEhq&amp;itok=EdXauVnj" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
